properties.description: The gripper of the robot. This specific model is a Robotiq 2F-85, meaning it has two fingers and has a grip range of 0 and 85 mmm.

A place for the human to conduct their own work.
A place for the human to walk.
Tool that attaches handles to the blade.
Machine that accepts blades from the conveyor.
Machine that moves finished knives to the next stage.
Machine that dispatches blades to the knife conveyor.
Tool that can serve as a sheath that makes the blade or knife safe to carry.
Sheaths the blade in a transport jig. Both must be present in appropriate orientation to occur.
Unsheaths the blade from a transport jig. Produces a blade and a transport jig.
Assembles a knife from two handles and a blade. All three must be present in appropriate orientation to occur.
Assembles a sheathed knife from two handles and a sheathed blade. All three must be present in appropriate orientation to occur.
